<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<%- include('../partials/head'); %>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-light navbar-expand-lg fixed-top" id="mainNav">
        <%- include('../partials/navigation.ejs'); %>
    </nav>
    
    <header class="masthead" style="background-image:url('assets/img/Background/BakeSale.jpg');">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                    <div class="site-heading">
                        <h1>Drug Purity Kits</h1><span class="subheading">Stay safe</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="container" style="background: #ffffff;">
        <section>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col col-md-4">
                    <p style="font-style: italic;"><em>Our Collective has raised funds to offer drug testing kits as a means of promoting a safer drug environment and reducing harm.&nbsp;</em><br></p>
                    <p><em>Following The Black Lives Matter</em><strong><em>&nbsp;</em></strong><em>movement,&nbsp;</em><strong><em>we have decided to match every kit offered with a donation to a BLM charity.</em></strong><br><br></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-8">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col"><img class="image" src="assets/img/PurityKits/KetamineTest.png" alt="Ketamine testing kit."></div>
                        <div class="col"><img class="image" src="assets/img/PurityKits/NarcoCheck.jpg" alt="Testing kits."></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col"><img class="image" src="assets/img/PurityKits/CocaineTest.png" alt="Cocaine testing kit."></div>
                        <div class="col"><img class="image" src="assets/img/PurityKits/EctasyTest.png" alt="Ectasy/MDMA testing kit."></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr style="background: rgb(0,0,0);border-width: 10px;">
        </section>
        <h2>Description</h2>
        <p style="margin: 0px;">Testing kits serve different purposes.</p>
        <section>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col col-md-8 column">
                            <h4>Ketamine Identification Test</h4>
                            <p style="margin-top: 0px;">Used for the identification of <strong>ketamine</strong>, <strong>methoxetamine</strong> (MXE), <strong>N-Ethyl-Ketamine</strong>, but also <strong>zolpidem</strong> (powerful somniferous).<br></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col col-md-4"><img class="image" src="assets/img/PurityKits/KetamineReferance.png"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col col-md-8 column">
                            <h4><strong>MDMA/ Ecstasy Identification Test</strong><br></h4>
                            <p style="margin-top: 0px;">Used for the identification of <strong>MDMA</strong> (the active principle of <strong>ecstasy</strong>) on powders and tablets.<br></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col col-md-4"><img class="image" src="assets/img/PurityKits/EctasyReferance.png"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col col-md-8 column">
                            <h4>Ketamine identification test:</h4>
                            <p style="margin-top: 0px;">Used for the identification of the main&nbsp;<strong>cocaine cutting agents,</strong>&nbsp;which can be very dangerous for health. These products include&nbsp;<strong>Levamisole</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>Ephedrine</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>Phenacetine</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>Lidocaine</strong>.<br></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col col-md-4"><img class="image" src="assets/img/PurityKits/CocaineReferance.png"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col column">
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong>These test can be done in 4 easy steps:</strong><br></p>
                            <ul class="list-group">
                                <li class="list-group-item"><span>1. Introduce a small amount of the drug into the test.<br></span></li>
                                <li class="list-group-item"><span>2.&nbsp;Introduce the catalyst found in the cap of the test.<br></span></li>
                                <li class="list-group-item"><span>3.&nbsp;The small particles or granules in the ampoule (the small sealed glass capsule) will change colour.<br></span></li>
                                <li class="list-group-item"><span>4.&nbsp;To examine results, please refer to the colour chart provided in the instructions.<br></span></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr style="background: rgb(0,0,0);border-width: 10px;">
        </section>
        <section>
            <p class="text-center" style="font-style: italic;"><strong><em>Following The Black Lives Matter movement,</em></strong><em> </em><strong><em>we have decided to match every kit offered with a donation to a BLM charity.</em></strong><br></p>
            <p class="text-center" style="font-style: italic;"><strong><em>All testing kits include £2.50 delivery fee.</em></strong><br></p>
        	
        	<div class="text-center" id="paypal-button"></div>
        </section>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <%- include('../partials/footer'); %>
    </footer>
    <div></div>
    <%- include('../partials/scripts'); %>
    <script src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/api/checkout.js"></script>
    
    <script>
    paypal.Button.render({
    	env: 'sandbox', // Or 'production'
    	// Set up the payment:
    	// 1. Add a payment callback
    	payment: function(data, actions) {
      	// 2. Make a request to your server
      		return actions.request.post('/my-api/create-payment/')
        	.then(function(res) {
          		// 3. Return res.id from the response
          		return res.id;
        	});
    	},
    	// Execute the payment:
   		// 1. Add an onAuthorize callback
    	onAuthorize: function(data, actions) {
      		// 2. Make a request to your server
      		return actions.request.post('/my-api/execute-payment/', {
        		paymentID: data.paymentID,
        		payerID:   data.payerID
      		})
        	.then(function(res) {
        		// 3. Show the buyer a confirmation message.
        	});
    	}
	}, '#paypal-button');
  	</script>
</body>

</html>